Industrial Engineer - Refinery Experience - Kansas

Graham & Associates

- Wichita, KS

Searching for an experienced Chemical Engineer with 5 or more years of experience. Need engineer who has experience with a variety of projects in industrial facilities, including chemical plants, refineries, etc. Evaluate processes and propose and design upgrades. Recommend and design updates to processes. Evaluate equipment, handle equipment selection. Work with vendors. Experience is a variety of industrial facilities is a plus in this position. Ability to work with clients is a must. Need engineer with strong communication skills, both written and verbal. Work as member of engineering team. Ability to work autonomously is needed. Handle field walk downs, project scope, proposals, design, commissioning, etc. Firm offers a variety of projects to work on as well as a strong compensation package. Please send resume as MS Word attachment. Resumes in MS Word attachment format will be opened, read and considered first. Thanks!
Job Type: Full-time
